<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/21 (Thu) Citizen Judges Act /Top 10 reasons to live in a retirement community (Host: Maggie)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=610&amp;p=633#p633"><![CDATA[
Citizen Judges Act /Top 10 reasons to live in a retirement community (Host: Maggie)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session I:<br />Citizen Judges Act<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://englishnews.ftv.com.tw/read.aspx?sno=67C9EA30050065F6D7A415736F9A09FB">https://englishnews.ftv.com.tw/read.asp ... 736F9A09FB</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br /><br />1. Do you agree with the national judge system? One day, if you are asked to serve, would you?<br />2. Who can be a national judge? <br />3. How to choose a national judge?<br />4. Protection and rights of national judges What should national judges do to participate in the trial of cases<br />5. How the process forms a judgment<br /><br /><br />Session II:<br />Top 10 reasons to live in a retirement community<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.seniorlifestyle.com/resources/blog/top-10-reasons-live-retirement-community/">https://www.seniorlifestyle.com/resourc ... community/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br /><br />1. Are you ready to retire? Or how old are you going to retire?<br />2. What are you going to do after retirement?<br />3. How much money do you think is enough to make your life happy and comfortable ?<br />4. When you are very old, would you like to go to a nursing home ? Or do you wish to live with children ?<br />5. How do you take care of yourself ? Is there a special tip that you  would like to share  with us ?<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Apr 15, 2022 9:31 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
